oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.dataSecurity.uiModel.util
Interface DataSecurityUIModelConstants

All Known Subinterfaces:
DataSecurityUIConstants
public interface DataSecurityUIModelConstants

Constants used for Data Security. Generic (utility) constants and functions. Other generic utility functions should be included here. All methods and members are static and do not need an instance of the class to use the methods.
